{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was always a petite girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while we were working over there, I had another incidence which was very rare, unusual.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As you know from the books and when you saw the movie, how Schindler was entertaining the highest Nazis, the murderers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by entertaining them, bribing them with diamonds, gold, the ladies and everything, he achieved this impossible, by doing those things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One day I was called-- not called, tapped on my shoulder by one of the managers-- and told-- ordered-- to follow him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told me to get washed the best way I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took me up to Schindler's apartment, where there was a party to be in the evening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- when I was brought up, the only Jewish girl over there, and they-- quickly, in the kitchen, whoever the manager was, they put on me a beautiful white apron.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was working all evening over there as helping in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "However, this is something unforgettable because I saw it with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I witnessed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After midnight, after the dinner, Schindler opened the huge doors with another Nazi man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a engineer in Schindler's factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They opened the huge door from the ballroom into the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they ordered all the help from the kitchen to enter the ballroom, like to get the thank you or applause from those Nazis for good service or for good food.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I could not believe what I saw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Number one, when you entered the ballroom, the-- the-- the chandeliers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The velvets.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you were blinded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then the music.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you saw the dozen of woman drinking with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were having the big party.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
